io.nebulas.account

Class KeyJSON

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.nebulas.account.KeyJSON

  • public class KeyJSON
extends java.lang.Object
    The KeyJson is the information for account wallet file. It contains the account address string, the crypt private key (by SCRYPT), the UUID, and the KeyJson version number.
